Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 早安 雷娅夫人 - 堂兄\N{\fs40}-Good morrow, Lady Rhea. -Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天的猎物是什么？兔子？\N{\fs40}What's today's quarry? Rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:07.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 鹿 - 不错的挑战\N{\fs40}-Deer. -Oh. Fine challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,需要人陪吗？\N{\fs40}Care for some company?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还是想自己去\N{\fs40}I'd rather ride alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝你好运咯\N{\fs40}Good fortune to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,丈夫\N{\fs40}Husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么风把你吹来谷地了？\N{\fs40}What brings you to the Vale?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:17.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难不成你终于要来圆房了？\N{\fs40}Or have you at last come to consummate our marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即使我不愿意\N{\fs40}The Vale's sheep might be willing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谷地的羊或许行\N{\fs40}even if I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们的羊还更好看呢\N{\fs40}Our sheep are prettier, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是说你哥哥终于受够了你在身边晃悠\N{\fs40}Or perhaps your brother has at last had his fill of your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为了个小姑娘把你丢一边了\N{\fs40}Cast you aside in favor of a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你现在要干嘛？\N{\fs40}What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,干掉那个孩子吗？\N{\fs40}Will you strike the child down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是……\N{\fs40}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我早就知道你最后一下不行\N{\fs40}I knew you couldn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,软蛋！\N{\fs40}Craven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:24.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs40}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs40}A moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想你离开\N{\fs40}I do not wish to see you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是国王的决定\N{\fs40}Such is the King's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最让我痛惜的决定\N{\fs40}A decision I most bitterly regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这是你造成的\N{\fs40}And yet, you made it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你选择了雷妮拉\N{\fs40}You chose Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她发誓她是清白的\N{\fs40}She swore her innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我相信她\N{\fs40}and I believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你想相信她 她父亲也是\N{\fs40}You wanted to believe her, as did her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的线人搞错了\N{\fs40}Your informant was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:44.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许是个无心之过 但我没想到会变成这样！\N{\fs40}An honest mistake, perhaps, but I did not foresee this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你应该想到的\N{\fs40}You should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:49.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还不是你非要坚持让伊耿当继承人！\N{\fs40}If you had not been so relentless in advancing Aegon as heir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听我说 女儿\N{\fs40}Listen to me, daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王迟早会死\N{\fs40}The King will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可能是几个月后 或是几年后 至少他不会活到老\N{\fs40}It may be months or years, but he'll not live to be an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果雷妮拉继承了王位\N{\fs40}And if Rhaenyra succeeds him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,战争会随之而来 你明白吗？\N{\fs40}war will follow, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个国家不会接受她\N{\fs40}The realm will not accept her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她为了确保自己的王位主张\N{\fs40}And to secure her claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会除掉你的孩子们\N{\fs40}she'll have to put your children to the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她到时候别无选择\N{\fs40}She'll have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你也知道的\N{\fs40}You know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不傻 但你选择无视事实\N{\fs40}You're no fool, and yet you choose not to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,时辰将至 阿莉森\N{\fs40}The time is coming, Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要么让伊耿做好登基的准备\N{\fs40}Either you prepare Aegon to rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要么就巴结雷妮拉 乞求她的怜悯\N{\fs40}or you cleave to Rhaenyra and pray for her mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人在哪？他应该等在这接待国王的\N{\fs40}Where is Lord Corlys? He should be here to receive the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到高潮城 陛下\N{\fs40}Welcome to High Tide, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思 兰娜尔小姐？\N{\fs40}What is the meaning of this, Lady Laena?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就是瓦列利安家族迎接国王的方式吗？\N{\fs40}Is this how House Velaryon greets its King?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的父亲刚结束长途旅行回到家中\N{\fs40}My father has but just returned from his long journey
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他已赶去九航厅\N{\fs40}and he has hastened to the Hall of Nine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在那里等待陛下的到来\N{\fs40}to await Your Grace's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,行了 我们走吧\N{\fs40}Let's just get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个外来的……\N{\fs40}An outsider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,混在土著里\N{\fs40}among the natives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拉里斯大人\N{\fs40}Lord Larys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,锦葵\N{\fs40}Malvales.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一种罕见的花\N{\fs40}A rare bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,原产于布拉佛斯\N{\fs40}Indigenous to Braavos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,按理说 它不可能在这里长得这么繁茂\N{\fs40}By all rights, it shouldn't be thriving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大自然 如此不可思议\N{\fs40}Nature, such mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 今天天气还不错 - 确实\N{\fs40}-The weather has been lovely. -Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而对这个国家来说却是黑暗的一天\N{\fs40}And yet it is a dark day for the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲是个好人\N{\fs40}Your father was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,取代他位置的你父亲也很好\N{\fs40}As is yours who took his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而\N{\fs40}Yet still,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲离任的方式……\N{\fs40}the manner of your father's departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:50.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让人觉得有些不公平\N{\fs40}it feels something of an injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,关于他离任的事情你知道什么？\N{\fs40}What do you know of the matter of his leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个从未被邀请发言的人\N{\fs40}When one is never invited to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会懂得……观察\N{\fs40}one learns instead to... observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你或许需要一个盟友？\N{\fs40}You're perhaps in need of an ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是王后\N{\fs40}I'm the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我不缺盟友 - 那是自然\N{\fs40}-I have no shortage of allies. -Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比如说雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenyra, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,讲清楚你的目的 大人\N{\fs40}State your purpose, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:20.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我确实好奇如今她是否还可以依赖\N{\fs40}I did wonder if she could be relied upon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为她身体有所不适\N{\fs40}now that she is unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不适？\N{\fs40}Unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可什么都没听说\N{\fs40}I haven't heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请原谅我 陛下 我可能搞错了\N{\fs40}Begging your pardon, Your Grace, I may be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:34.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在您父亲被革职的那晚\N{\fs40}It's just that on the very same night your father was dismissed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:38.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大学士给公主的房间里送去了一碗茶\N{\fs40}the Grand Maester delivered a tea to the Princess's chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 一碗茶？ - 是的\N{\fs40}-A tea? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大学士自己安排的？\N{\fs40}That the Grand Maester himself brought?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:50.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据我所知 是国王的命令\N{\fs40}At the direction of the King, as I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我倒是希望她没有什么不适\N{\fs40}I do hope she's not unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉陪国王坐船去潮头岛了\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra sailed with the King to Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 昨天黎明时分出发的 - 这可是个好消息\N{\fs40}-yesterday at daybreak. -Oh what good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一定搞错了\N{\fs40}I must've been in error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可松了口气\N{\fs40}Oh, a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瞧 我原以为梅罗斯亲自出马的话……\N{\fs40}See, I thought for Mellos himself, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那她的病情一定很严重\N{\fs40}her condition must be something very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:19.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,发现自己搞错了的感觉真好\N{\fs40}What happiness it is to have been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs40}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来 表姐\N{\fs40}Come, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱们去看看早餐都有什么\N{\fs40}Let us discover what might be had for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起身 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}Rise, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fs40}Be welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给您拿把椅子？\N{\fs40}May I offer you a chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:54.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,堂弟！\N{\fs40}Cousin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗？ - 非常好\N{\fs40}-Are you well? -Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 莱昂诺大人\N{\fs40}I congratulate you, Lord Lyonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想象不到还有谁比你更适合担任国王之手\N{\fs40}I can think of no man more suited to be the Hand of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢夸奖 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}That is very kind of you to say, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下授予我这个职位是我的荣幸\N{\fs40}His Grace has honored me with the post.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对奥托爵士深表遗憾\N{\fs40}Pity about Ser Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽管我大部分时间都在宏伟的红堡中度过\N{\fs40}Despite spending most of my days amidst the grandeur of the Red Keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,高潮城的厅堂总能让我印象深刻\N{\fs40}the halls of High Tide never fail to impress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您过奖了 陛下\N{\fs40}You flatter me, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过我的确希望我们能在更愉快的氛围下见面\N{\fs40}Though I do wish we could meet under happier pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 怎么说？ - 戴蒙的妻子\N{\fs40}-How so? -Daemon's wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅·罗伊斯夫人 过世了\N{\fs40}the Lady Rhea Royce, has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打猎事故\N{\fs40}A hunting mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她从马背上摔下来\N{\fs40}She was thrown from her horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这一摔 把脖子和头骨都摔碎了\N{\fs40}Her neck and skull both crushed in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让人惊讶的死法\N{\fs40}A most surprising end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:57.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅夫人骑马和打猎的高超技术众人皆知\N{\fs40}Lady Rhea's skill as both rider and hunter were well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 七神残忍 - 的确\N{\fs40}-The gods are cruel. -Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:06.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅夫人是个优秀的女人 也是我弟弟的良配\N{\fs40}Lady Rhea was a fine woman and a good wife to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可惜她和戴蒙没有继承人\N{\fs40}Sad thing that she and Daemon have no heirs to succeed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她有符石城的继承权\N{\fs40}She stood to inherit Runestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们来聊聊开心些的话题吧\N{\fs40}Mayhaps we can turn toward happier pursuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不了 谢谢 - 您想说什么 陛下？\N{\fs40}-No, thank you. -What did you have in mind, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想撮合一段婚姻 你的儿子 兰尼诺爵士……\N{\fs40}I wish to propose a marriage between your son, Ser Laenor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:31.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与我的女儿及继承人 雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}and my daughter and heir, the Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们两家早就应该血脉相连了\N{\fs40}It's long past time our houses were united in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为古瓦雷利亚最后的支柱\N{\fs40}The last pillars of Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:41.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这对我和我的家族都是巨大的荣幸 陛下\N{\fs40}You honor both me and my house, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:44.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过有一些细节我希望能确定\N{\fs40}There are certain details I would wish clarified
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在雷妮丝公主和我接受这最……\N{\fs40}before the Princess Rhaenys and I could accept this most...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,慷慨的提议前说清\N{\fs40}generous proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么细节？\N{\fs40}What details?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们想要了解您如何处理继承人的事宜\N{\fs40}We would like to know how the succession will be handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉是我的继承人\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra is my heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我死后 我的王位和头衔会传给她\N{\fs40}Upon my death, my throne and my titles will pass to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她与兰尼诺爵士的第一个孩子 无论男女\N{\fs40}She and Ser Laenor's firstborn child, regardless of gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都会从她的手里接过王位\N{\fs40}will inherit the Iron Throne from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:21.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是否可以假设 按照维斯特洛的传统…\N{\fs40}Can I presume that, in keeping with Westerosi tradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们的孩子会冠以父亲的姓氏？\N{\fs40}their children would take their father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也就是姓瓦列利安？\N{\fs40}That they would be born Velaryons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯伯爵\N{\fs40}Surely, Lord Corlys,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难道你以为坦格利安王朝将在我女儿这代结束\N{\fs40}you are not proposing the Targaryen dynasty end with my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,仅仅因为她是女人？\N{\fs40}simply because she is a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是想澄清细节 陛下\N{\fs40}I only seek clarity, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 要不还是拿把椅子吧？ - 我不…\N{\fs40}-Might I have a chair brought in for you? -I do not--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 我不需要椅子\N{\fs40}No. I do not require a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:59.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺爵士和雷妮拉的孩子们一出生\N{\fs40}Upon their birth, Ser Laenor and Rhaenyra's children
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就会冠以父亲的姓氏 也就是瓦列利安…\N{\fs40}shall take their father's name, Velaryon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以维护我们的传统\N{\fs40}in keeping with our traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs40}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:11.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当他们的头生子登上铁王座之时\N{\fs40}at such time when their firstborn ascends the Iron Throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论男女 都会改为坦格利安\N{\fs40}he or she will do so bearing the name Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:20.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙王家族在七大王国的统治将再延续一个世纪\N{\fs40}Dragons will rule the Seven Kingdoms for the next hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如之前那个世纪一样\N{\fs40}just as they did the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,非常公平的折中\N{\fs40}This is an equitable compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs40}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果没别的事 就到此为止\N{\fs40}Now, if there's nothing further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:58.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说实话 非得与谁成婚的话 我很高兴这个人是你\N{\fs40}In truth, if it had to be someone, I'm glad it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我明白 这场联姻不是出自你的真心\N{\fs40}I know this union is not what you would choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对你没有意见 表姐\N{\fs40}I hold nothing against you, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 我——\N{\fs40}No, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,宁愿……\N{\fs40}rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:16.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可不可以把这比喻成个人口味？\N{\fs40}Dare I say it is a matter of taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比起烧鹅 我更喜欢烤鸭\N{\fs40}I prefer roast duck to goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说不出为什么\N{\fs40}I cannot say why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,其实不是因为没试过\N{\fs40}It's not for a lack of trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有些人生来就是喜欢烧鹅\N{\fs40}There are those who like goose very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对我个人口味而言 烧鹅有些油腻\N{\fs40}I find it a bit greasy for my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论我们的父辈达成何种协议\N{\fs40}I know that whatever agreement being struck up there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都不会改变你的口味\N{\fs40}will not change your appetites,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也如此\N{\fs40}nor will it change mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么 你有什么提议？\N{\fs40}And what do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:03.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们为父辈及国家履行自己的责任\N{\fs40}That we perform our duty to our fathers and to the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,完事之后…\N{\fs40}and when it's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们可以依照各自的口味用餐\N{\fs40}each of us dines as we see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:22.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯已经上床休息了 船正准备起航\N{\fs40}Viserys has taken to bed while his ship is readied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许我……\N{\fs40}Perhaps I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要得太多了？\N{\fs40}overextended myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把他逼得太狠？\N{\fs40}Pushed him too close to the edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的堂弟选择了驶入这场风暴 夫君\N{\fs40}My cousin chose to sail into this tempest, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王亲自前来 请求与兰尼诺的婚约\N{\fs40}It was undignified of the King to drag himself here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这已有失尊严\N{\fs40}and beg for Laenor's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺在哪儿？\N{\fs40}Where is Laenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他和雷妮拉在海滩散步 - 很好\N{\fs40}-He and Rhaenyra are walking the coast. -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们看上去……亲近吗？\N{\fs40}Do they seem... familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们从小一起长大\N{\fs40}They grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲近不成问题\N{\fs40}Familiarity is not at issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定 兰尼诺已经被雷妮拉迷住了\N{\fs40}I'm sure Laenor was already taken with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这几年 她是越来越漂亮了\N{\fs40}She's grown quite comely these last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道他的本性\N{\fs40}You know his true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他还年轻\N{\fs40}He's still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会长大的\N{\fs40}He will outgrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这世上哪有什么乐子……\N{\fs40}There is no pleasure in the world like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比得了跟女人上床\N{\fs40}bedding a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:20.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是把我们的儿子置于险境\N{\fs40}We are placing our son in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七大王国的领主们向雷妮拉屈膝下跪\N{\fs40}The lords of the realm bent the knee to Rhaenyra
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,向她效忠\N{\fs40}and swore obeisance to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是在真正的王子出生之前\N{\fs40}That was before there was a true-born prince
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而他名叫伊耿·坦格利安\N{\fs40}named Aegon Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉的继承权将会受到挑战\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra's succession will be challenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:35.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她 她的丈夫 以及他们的孩子 必然要面临刀剑的威胁\N{\fs40}Knives will come out for her, her husband, and for their heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:39.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们家族控制着全国的海军以及一半的龙\N{\fs40}Our house controls the realm's navy and half its dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁若蠢到挑战雷妮拉的继承权\N{\fs40}Anyone fool enough to challenge Rhaenyra's claim
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 只会被碾碎 - 为了什么 科利斯 财富？权力？\N{\fs40}-will be crushed. -To what end, Corlys? Wealth? Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 自尊？ - 公正\N{\fs40}-Pride? -Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管按什么法理\N{\fs40}By all rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都应该是你成为七大王国的女王\N{\fs40}you should be Queen of the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抢走你王冠的人就是——\N{\fs40}You were robbed of the crown by--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:03.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从未戴上王冠 因为七大王国不会允许此事发生\N{\fs40}I never wore the crown because the realm would not have it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以弥补这个\N{\fs40}And I would remedy that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狭隘的错误 用上一切必要的手——\N{\fs40}small-minded error by any means necessar--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:13.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我早就不想这事了 科利斯\N{\fs40}I myself have put the business behind me, Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直不敢面对你不得不娶妻的那天\N{\fs40}I've always feared the day you'd have to marry a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在 这天要来了\N{\fs40}And now it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的未婚妻自愿允许你\N{\fs40}Your betrothed gives you leave
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继续享用大餐\N{\fs40}of her own free will to continue partaking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是烤鸭还是烧鹅来着？\N{\fs40}Was I the duck or the goose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我过来直面命运 你却拿它开起了玩笑？\N{\fs40}I've come to meet my fate and you make a jape of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听着 雷妮拉会成为七大王国的女王\N{\fs40}Look, Rhaenyra will be Queen of the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:44.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而你会是她的王夫\N{\fs40}and you will be her king consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想想比武大会\N{\fs40}Think of the tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,盛宴 还有海战吧\N{\fs40}the feast, the battles at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:55.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您今天会戴上王冠吗？陛下\N{\fs40}Will you wear your crown today, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,傻子\N{\fs40}You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你得有个贴身护卫\N{\fs40}You will need a sworn protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:32.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这远比我们预想的要好\N{\fs40}This is better than we could've hoped for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:39.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她有自己的情人\N{\fs40}She has a paramour of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:43.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我好奇他是谁\N{\fs40}I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一大清早 你也睡不着吗？\N{\fs40}Did sleep flee you as well this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要见您 公主殿下\N{\fs40}I needed to see you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:15.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦白地说 我也是\N{\fs40}I confess I had a similar desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:25.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们相识的这些年里 您时不时向我吐露心声\N{\fs40}You have confided in me now and then over the years of our acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:32.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我猜 恕我冒昧 我多少……了解您一点\N{\fs40}I feel, forgive me, that I, I know you... a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你了解的可不止一点\N{\fs40}You know more than a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:45.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我总听您说 您有多么厌恶身居高位所要面对的命运\N{\fs40}I've heard you say so many times how you loathe the lot of your position,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:47.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您反感父亲心血来潮的婚约指命\N{\fs40}that you are to be married off at your father's whim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,完全没考虑您内心的渴望\N{\fs40}with no thought given to the yearning of your own heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:53.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而 这一天还是来了\N{\fs40}and now the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:58.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然兰尼诺爵士善良正直 但您……并没有选他\N{\fs40}Ser Laenor is a good and, and decent man, but you, you did not choose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:03.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有人为您做了选择 - 你说的对\N{\fs40}-He was chosen for you. -That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:08.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倘若还有另一条路……\N{\fs40}If there were another path...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:11.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,能通往自由……\N{\fs40}one that led to freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您愿意走吗？\N{\fs40}would you tread it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉 我来君临之前\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra, before I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:20.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是风暴地的骑士\N{\fs40}I was a knight in the Stormlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:23.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很了解阳戟城的港口\N{\fs40}I have deep knowledge of the port at Sunspear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:25.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾在那儿见过厄斯索斯的商船扬帆起航\N{\fs40}where I've seen the ships of Essos setting sail
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:27.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,满载橙子和肉桂而归\N{\fs40}with their hulls full of oranges and cinnamon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:30.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直希望能看看那些船航向了哪里\N{\fs40}and I've always wished to see where they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想要告假吗？\N{\fs40}Are you asking for leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:37.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是想请求你跟我走……\N{\fs40}I'm asking you to come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:41.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,远离这一切\N{\fs40}away from all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.86,0:24:44.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,离开继承人身份带来的负担和侮辱\N{\fs40}From the burdens and indignities of your inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:48.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们抛下这一切 一起去探索这个世界……\N{\fs40}Let us leave it all behind and see the world together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:51.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们可以隐姓埋名\N{\fs40}where we'll be nameless,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.70,0:24:53.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自由自在……\N{\fs40}and free...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.24,0:24:56.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去任何我们想去的地方 无所顾忌地相爱\N{\fs40}free to go where we like, to love as we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.46,0:25:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在厄斯索斯……\N{\fs40}In Essos...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.67,0:25:04.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你可以嫁给我\N{\fs40}you could marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.17,0:25:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为了爱情而结婚\N{\fs40}A marriage for love,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.05,0:25:11.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而不是为了王位\N{\fs40}not for the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:39.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我就是王 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I am the crown, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.12,0:25:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者说我会成王\N{\fs40}Or I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.21,0:25:47.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可能会厌烦职责\N{\fs40}I may chafe at my duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:51.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你以为我会选择身败名裂\N{\fs40}but do you think I would choose infamy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:54.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就为了一筐橙子或是一张航向亚夏的船票吗？\N{\fs40}in exchange for a bushel of oranges or a ship to Asshai?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:25:59.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的责任就是\N{\fs40}It is my duty
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:02.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与一位豪门贵族结婚\N{\fs40}to marry a nobleman from a great house
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.85,0:26:05.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺爵士会是一个好丈夫\N{\fs40}and Ser Laenor will make a fine husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.86,0:26:11.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是我的……\N{\fs40}But my...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.78,0:26:14.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的婚姻……\N{\fs40}my marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.74,0:26:17.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并不意味着我们关系的终结\N{\fs40}does not have to be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士 兰尼诺和我达成了共识\N{\fs40}Ser Criston, Laenor and I have an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:31.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我允许他去追求自己的兴趣……\N{\fs40}I've granted him leave to pursue his own interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.47,0:26:34.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为回报 他也给予我同样的自由\N{\fs40}and in turn, he's granted me the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.68,0:26:43.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你想要我当你的婊子？\N{\fs40}So you want me to be your whore?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:48.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想要我们像一开始那样\N{\fs40}I want us to continue as we began,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.94,0:26:52.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是我的贴身护卫 我的白骑士\N{\fs40}with you as my sworn protector, my white knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.65,0:26:54.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我立过誓的\N{\fs40}I took an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.28,0:26:59.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为御林铁卫的骑士\N{\fs40}As a, as a knight of, of your Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.74,0:27:01.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾发誓守贞 我打破了这个誓言\N{\fs40}An oath of chastity. I've broken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.79,0:27:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我不会告诉任何人—— - 我 我玷污了我的 我的白——我的白袍\N{\fs40}-I won't tell anyone-- -I've, I've soiled my, my, wh-- my white cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.29,0:27:07.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我他妈名下唯一的东西\N{\fs40}And it's the only thing I have to my fucking name!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.88,0:27:13.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以为如果我们结婚了 也许我能挽回荣誉\N{\fs40}I thought if we were married, I might be able to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:22.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,铁王座比我更重要\N{\fs40}The Iron Throne looms larger than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.39,0:27:25.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比我家族中任何人都更重要\N{\fs40}larger than anyone in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.02,0:27:29.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者伊耿统一了七国\N{\fs40}Aegon the Conqueror united the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.73,0:27:31.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让它走上了一条——\N{\fs40}and put them on a path--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.44,0:27:33.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:23.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 去找学士 - 退后\N{\fs40}-Fetch the Maester! -Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.24,0:28:24.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去找梅罗斯！退后！\N{\fs40}Get Mellos! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.08,0:28:26.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,准备坩埚\N{\fs40}Prepare the crucible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:29.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去找水蛭\N{\fs40}We'll need leeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.59,0:28:34.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士……\N{\fs40}Ser Criston...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.42,0:28:37.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您被传唤了\N{\fs40}you've been summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.22,0:28:41.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我刚刚才离开公主\N{\fs40}I left the Princess just minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.35,0:28:43.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是公主 爵士\N{\fs40}Not the Princess, ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:45.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是王后\N{\fs40}The Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.61,0:29:02.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士来了 陛下\N{\fs40}Ser Criston, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.54,0:29:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,退下吧\N{\fs40}That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.13,0:29:24.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐怕我得问你一件 一件敏感的事情 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I fear I must question you on a, on a delicate matter, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.10,0:29:30.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一贯是您的仆人 王后\N{\fs40}I am your servant as always, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:33.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这关系到我们亲爱的公主雷妮拉\N{\fs40}It concerns our dear Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs40}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.72,0:30:05.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是她的贴身护卫 自然是对她忠诚的\N{\fs40}You are her sworn protector and rightly loyal to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.10,0:30:08.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.52,0:30:14.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙回来的那晚……\N{\fs40}The night of Daemon's return...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.23,0:30:18.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有一个传言……\N{\fs40}there's been a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.78,0:30:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者说 我父亲收到了一份……\N{\fs40}or rather, my father received an accounting of...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:28.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,某人行为失当的报告\N{\fs40}a lapse of morals
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:32.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许是发生在——\N{\fs40}that may have occurred between--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.75,0:30:38.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 我觉得质疑公主的德行是不可思议的\N{\fs40}It is, of course, unthinkable for me to question the virtue of the Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.00,0:30:40.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一向十分敬重公主\N{\fs40}whom I hold in highest regard,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:45.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我——我确实想过 如果……\N{\fs40}but I-I, I did, however, wonder if...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:55.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不是不知道在年轻的冲动下……\N{\fs40}I'm not unaware that in flush of youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.90,0:30:58.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许会犯下一些错误……\N{\fs40}there may be errors made...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.90,0:31:02.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,决定违背……\N{\fs40}breaches in resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.57,0:31:04.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,违背 或者说疏忽——\N{\fs40}breaches, or rather lapses--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.49,0:31:05.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确有此事 陛下\N{\fs40}It happened, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.24,0:31:13.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您所暗示的罪行\N{\fs40}The sin you allude to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.29,0:31:17.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我犯的\N{\fs40}I have committed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:24.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实是在她的挑逗下 但是那不应该——\N{\fs40}At her instigation, it is true, but that should--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.59,0:31:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没有借口\N{\fs40}It is no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.10,0:31:31.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我背了誓\N{\fs40}My oath has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.77,0:31:34.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我使自己蒙羞\N{\fs40}I have dishonored myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.06,0:31:37.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不值得体谅\N{\fs40}I deserve no consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.23,0:31:43.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果……\N{\fs40}But if...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:48.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为一位仁慈的王后 若您有意怜悯……\N{\fs40}as a clement Queen, you are inclined to pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:51.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只请求……\N{\fs40}I would ask only this...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:57.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与其阉割我\N{\fs40}that rather than gelding me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.25,0:31:59.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,折磨我\N{\fs40}and having me tortured
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.21,0:32:03.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不如仁慈地判决我死刑\N{\fs40}you would sentence me mercifully to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:21.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢你的坦诚 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Thank you for your honesty, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.37,0:32:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\fs40}You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.65,0:33:07.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧 陛下 我会拿水蛭来\N{\fs40}Rest now, Your Grace. I will bring the leeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.94,0:33:09.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧 大学士\N{\fs40}If I may, Grand Maester,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.07,0:33:13.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我自作主张准备了一副新的\N{\fs40}I took the liberty of preparing a fresh set
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.70,0:33:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许会更有效的草药膏\N{\fs40}of herbal poultices that might be more effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.83,0:33:20.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不需要 欧维尔\N{\fs40}That will not be necessary, Orwyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.46,0:33:24.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,水蛭一向能使陛下放松\N{\fs40}The leechings have always brought His Grace relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:45.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个能帮他入睡\N{\fs40}To help him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.66,0:33:56.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后呢？\N{\fs40}Where's the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.58,0:34:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据我所知她另有他事 陛下\N{\fs40}I was given to understand that she is otherwise occupied, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.10,0:34:25.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会作为一个好国王流芳百世吗 莱昂诺？\N{\fs40}Will I be remembered as a good king, Lyonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.32,0:34:28.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下？\N{\fs40}Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.61,0:34:33.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,史书里会怎样评价我呢？\N{\fs40}What will they say of me when the histories are written?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.07,0:34:36.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我既没有战斗过 也没有征服过\N{\fs40}I have neither fought nor conquered,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.74,0:34:38.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没有遭受过重大的失败\N{\fs40}nor suffered any great defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:43.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有些人会说这是福气\N{\fs40}Some might call that good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.17,0:34:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这可不好写歌谣啊 是不是？\N{\fs40}It hardly makes a good song, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:52.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,能在一百年 五百年后的宴会上\N{\fs40}To be sung at feasts in a hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.13,0:34:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,唱起的歌谣\N{\fs40}five hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.09,0:34:59.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您继承了杰赫里斯国王的遗志\N{\fs40}You have carried King Jaehaerys's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:03.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,维持王国长盛不衰\N{\fs40}And kept the realm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:05.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,生活在和平当中\N{\fs40}Is it not better to live in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:08.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不比死后有歌谣传颂更好吗？\N{\fs40}than to have songs sung after you are dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:10.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\fs40}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.61,0:35:15.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我有点渴望经历考验\N{\fs40}But there is a part of me wishes I'd been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:19.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我总觉得在坩埚之中\N{\fs40}I often think that in the crucible,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.78,0:35:22.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也许会被铸造成一个不同的人\N{\fs40}I may have been forged a different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.33,0:35:28.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很多遭受考验的人 只希望能免于此难\N{\fs40}Many that are tested, only wish to have been spared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.13,0:35:33.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要是换个人 说不定会向我保证\N{\fs40}Another lord might assure me that I would rise like
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.01,0:35:35.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假以时机我可以像征服者伊耿一样雄起\N{\fs40}Aegon the Conqueror given the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.97,0:35:37.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下 这是—— - 你是对的\N{\fs40}-Your Grace, that is-- -You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.26,0:35:41.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你总是对的\N{\fs40}You're right as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.98,0:35:46.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许 最好还是别知道答案了\N{\fs40}It is perhaps best not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:36.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怀着极其喜悦的心情\N{\fs40}It is with great pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.40,0:36:39.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯国王陛下宣布\N{\fs40}that His Grace, King Viserys, announces the start
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王家婚礼庆典正式开始\N{\fs40}of the royal wedding celebrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.33,0:36:48.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼斯特家族及其领主 杰森·兰尼斯特\N{\fs40}House Lannister with their lord, Jason Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.71,0:36:52.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,西境总督 凯岩城之主\N{\fs40}Lord Paramount of the West, and Master of Casterly Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.00,0:36:57.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海塔尔家族及其领主 霍巴特·海塔尔\N{\fs40}House Hightower with their lord, Hobert Hightower.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.72,0:37:00.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,南境之灯塔 学城的守护者\N{\fs40}Beacon of the South, Defender of the Citadel,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.97,0:37:02.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,旧镇之音……\N{\fs40}the Voice of Oldtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.11,0:37:16.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恭喜 陛下\N{\fs40}Congratulations, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:19.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您为公主找到了佳偶\N{\fs40}You have made a fine match for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.40,0:37:20.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 杰森公爵\N{\fs40}Thank you, Lord Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.07,0:37:23.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想不到比兰尼诺爵士更好的人选了\N{\fs40}I could think of no better man than Ser Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.58,0:37:27.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果接风宴就已经这样了\N{\fs40}Well, if this is only the welcome feast,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.33,0:37:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,得承认 我想不出您为婚礼准备了什么\N{\fs40}I admit, I cannot imagine what you might have planned for the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.92,0:37:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我女儿是未来的女王\N{\fs40}My daughter is the future queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.46,0:37:37.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望这场婚礼是史无前例的\N{\fs40}I wanted this to be a wedding for the histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.80,0:37:40.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后在哪里呢？\N{\fs40}Where is the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.26,0:37:42.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想要致以敬意\N{\fs40}I had hoped to pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.01,0:37:48.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说王后仍然在为出席庆典做准备\N{\fs40}I understand the Queen is still readying herself for the celebrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.27,0:37:50.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就是男人才能开战的原因\N{\fs40}This is why men wage war
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.27,0:37:53.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,女人永远不会及时做好战斗准备\N{\fs40}because women would never be ready for the battle in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.90,0:38:01.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的到来总是那么令人愉悦 杰森公爵\N{\fs40}Your presence is always such a pleasure, Lord Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:04.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 陛下 告退\N{\fs40}Princess, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 雷妮拉公主 恭喜\N{\fs40}Your Grace, Princess Rhaenyra, congratulations are in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.76,0:38:22.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们非常荣幸你来做客 杰洛爵士\N{\fs40}We are very honored to have you as a guest, Ser Gerold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.63,0:38:24.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不得不说\N{\fs40}I must say, I was most distressed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.68,0:38:27.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅夫人不幸去世的消息让我非常悲痛\N{\fs40}to hear of the Lady Rhea's tragic passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.47,0:38:30.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请你节哀顺变\N{\fs40}I'm very sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.18,0:38:32.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅夫人是位独特的人\N{\fs40}Lady Rhea was a unique character.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.06,0:38:36.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们将难得再见如此之人\N{\fs40}Her kind is not soon to be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:39.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果王室有什么能帮助罗伊斯家族的——\N{\fs40}If there is anything the crown might do to aid House Royce--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:50.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的科利斯伯爵\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys of House Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.79,0:38:53.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮汛之主 潮头岛之主\N{\fs40}Lord of the Tides, Master of Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.83,0:38:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他的夫人 雷妮丝·坦格利安公主\N{\fs40}And his lady wife, Princess Rhaenys Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.38,0:39:00.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及他们的儿子兼继承人 兰尼诺·瓦列利安爵士\N{\fs40}And their son and heir, Ser Laenor Velaryon,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:03.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,未来的王夫\N{\fs40}the future king consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.84,0:39:47.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-我的未婚夫 -我的未婚妻\N{\fs40}-My Betrothed. -My Betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.89,0:41:14.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位莅临庆典\N{\fs40}Be welcome, as we join together in celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.27,0:41:17.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今夜只是开始\N{\fs40}Tonight is only its beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.73,0:41:21.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们向王室最古老\N{\fs40}We honor the crown's oldest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.40,0:41:24.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也是最有力的盟友瓦列利安家族致敬\N{\fs40}and fiercest ally, House Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.07,0:41:32.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们可追溯到古瓦雷利亚和巨龙纪元\N{\fs40}Reaching back to the days of Old Valyria and the Age of Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.91,0:41:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在坦格利安家族和……\N{\fs40}With House Targaryen and--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.74,0:42:17.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王肯定不高兴了\N{\fs40}The King will not be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.49,0:42:19.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,话说一半被打断\N{\fs40}Right in the midst of his speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.88,0:42:33.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当旧镇召集封臣开战时\N{\fs40}The beacon on the Hightower,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.34,0:42:37.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道参天塔的灯火是什么颜色吗？\N{\fs40}do you know what color it glows when Oldtown calls its banners to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:39.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绿色\N{\fs40}Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:53.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恭喜 我的继女\N{\fs40}Congratulations, stepdaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:55.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这真是你的好福气\N{\fs40}What a blessing this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:09.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请就座\N{\fs40}Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.39,0:43:19.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说到哪了？\N{\fs40}Where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.85,0:43:21.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,两大家族的结合 陛下\N{\fs40}The joining of the two houses, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.85,0:43:23.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:25.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.61,0:43:37.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家族和瓦列利安家族即将联合\N{\fs40}With House Targaryen and House Velaryon united,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.28,0:43:42.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望这昭示着维斯特洛的第二个巨龙纪元\N{\fs40}I hope to herald in a second Age of Dragons in Westeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:57.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在今夜的小场面之后……\N{\fs40}And after tonight's small affair...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.01,0:44:02.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会有七天的比武和盛宴\N{\fs40}seven days of tournament and feasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.60,0:44:07.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最后……\N{\fs40}At the end of it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.40,0:44:11.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最后是……王室婚礼……\N{\fs40}At the end of it all, a royal wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.65,0:44:14.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,缔结了我的爱女\N{\fs40}between my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.19,0:44:16.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的继承人\N{\fs40}my heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.15,0:44:18.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们未来的女王\N{\fs40}your future Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.66,0:44:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与潮头岛继承人 兰尼诺·瓦列利安爵士\N{\fs40}and Ser Laenor Velaryon, the heir to Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.26,0:45:17.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一向不擅长跳舞\N{\fs40}I was never much of a dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.92,0:45:19.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这和打架没什么区别\N{\fs40}It's not much different to combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.30,0:45:21.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望结果会有所不同\N{\fs40}I shall hope for a different outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.63,0:46:39.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下 - 伯伯 感谢光临\N{\fs40}-Your Grace. -We thank you for coming, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.09,0:46:41.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我原本担心你离开父亲的庇护\N{\fs40}I worried that given leave of your father's shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.80,0:46:45.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会在君临的烈日下枯萎\N{\fs40}you might wither in King's Landing's sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.14,0:46:47.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你身姿傲然\N{\fs40}But you stood tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.35,0:46:50.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,记住 旧镇与你同在\N{\fs40}Know that Oldtown stands with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.46,0:47:22.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在谷地 人们必须为自己的罪行负责\N{\fs40}In the Vale, men are made to answer for their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.97,0:47:25.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至坦格利安族人也不例外\N{\fs40}Even Targaryens.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.34,0:47:27.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fs40}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.39,0:47:30.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,符石城的杰洛·罗伊斯爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Gerold Royce of Runestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.14,0:47:33.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后呢？\N{\fs40}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.23,0:47:45.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是你已故夫人的堂兄\N{\fs40}I am cousin to your late lady wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.90,0:47:49.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错 真可怕\N{\fs40}Yes. Terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.12,0:47:52.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我极度悲伤 多么悲惨的意外\N{\fs40}I'm positively bereft. Such a tragic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.49,0:47:55.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你比任何人都清楚 这不是意外\N{\fs40}You know better than anyone, it was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.54,0:47:57.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是来认罪的吗 杰洛爵士？\N{\fs40}Are you confessing some guilt, Ser Gerold?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.58,0:48:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是控诉的\N{\fs40}I am making an accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.09,0:48:06.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在君临 人们必须为自己的诽谤负责\N{\fs40}In King's Landing, men are made to answer for their slanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.59,0:48:08.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至你这样的老青铜婊子也不例外\N{\fs40}Even old bronze cunts like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.97,0:48:12.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事实上 我很高兴你能来\N{\fs40}The truth is, I'm glad you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.35,0:48:14.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想和你谈谈我的继承问题\N{\fs40}I wish to speak to you about my inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.85,0:48:18.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 什么继承问题？ - 雷娅夫人和我没有子嗣\N{\fs40}-What inheritance? -Lady Rhea and I had no heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.90,0:48:22.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为她的丈夫 她的一切权利现在都传承给我了\N{\fs40}As her husband, whatever she was due now passes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.78,0:48:28.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她将继承符石城的一切 对吧？\N{\fs40}She stood to inherit all of Runestone. Did she not?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.74,0:48:33.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我侄女完婚后 我会飞到鹰巢城\N{\fs40}After my niece's wedding, I plan to fly to the Eyrie
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.99,0:48:35.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲自向简妮夫人请愿\N{\fs40}and petition Lady Jeyne myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.62,0:48:37.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许我们能在那里再碰面 杰洛爵士\N{\fs40}Perhaps I'll see you there, Ser Gerold.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.66,0:49:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人告诉过你 你几乎和你哥哥一样漂亮吗？\N{\fs40}Has anybody ever told you you're nearly as pretty as your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.20,0:49:57.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你过誉了 王子\N{\fs40}You flatter me, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.58,0:50:00.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 听说你夫人的事我很难过 - 不用难过 我不伤心\N{\fs40}-I was sorry to hear about your lady wife. -Don't be, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.21,0:50:02.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的夫人对我从来都不是很好\N{\fs40}My lady was never very kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.92,0:50:04.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道是谁了\N{\fs40}I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.59,0:50:07.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个英俊的情人\N{\fs40}The handsome paramour.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.63,0:50:08.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁？\N{\fs40}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.55,0:50:11.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿·科尔爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Criston Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.93,0:50:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的贴身护卫？\N{\fs40}Her sworn protector?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.93,0:50:15.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看看他\N{\fs40}Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.22,0:50:18.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,被迷得神魂颠倒\N{\fs40}The man is fully cunt-struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.10,0:50:22.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安王子 勇猛的骑士和驭龙者\N{\fs40}A Targaryen prince, a dashing knight, and a dragonrider.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.27,0:50:23.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你似乎是每个少女的梦想\N{\fs40}You appear to be every young maiden's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.98,0:50:25.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那只是因为你还不了解我\N{\fs40}That's only because you don't know me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.02,0:50:28.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信克里斯顿爵士的白袍上\N{\fs40}I believe Ser Criston has bloodied that white cloak of his
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.48,0:50:29.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,沾染了你新娘的处子血\N{\fs40}with your bride's maidenhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.82,0:50:30.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小点声\N{\fs40}Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.90,0:50:33.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以为此补救 王子\N{\fs40}Perhaps that is something we might remedy, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.20,0:50:34.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fs40}Perhaps it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.70,0:50:39.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是件好事 她知道你的秘密\N{\fs40}This is a good thing. She knows your secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.62,0:50:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在你也知道她的\N{\fs40}and now you know hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.21,0:50:48.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.84,0:50:55.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.85,0:50:58.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.90,0:51:05.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:08.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.44,0:51:13.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们真是天造地设的一对 是吧？\N{\fs40}They make a handsome match, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.36,0:51:15.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs40}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.45,0:51:18.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主和兰尼诺爵士\N{\fs40}The Princess and Ser Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.83,0:51:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.04,0:51:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在下乔佛里·隆莫斯爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Joffrey Lonmouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.63,0:51:32.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人称“热吻骑士”\N{\fs40}or the Knight of Kisses, they call me,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.55,0:51:34.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不知道为什么这么叫我\N{\fs40}though I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.63,0:51:37.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在值守 有何贵干？\N{\fs40}I'm on watch. What's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.39,0:51:40.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不认识我 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}You don't know me, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.18,0:51:42.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们都深深纠缠在这场联姻中\N{\fs40}But we are both deeply invested in this union.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.85,0:51:43.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.73,0:51:48.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,乔佛里爵士 如果你有话不妨直说\N{\fs40}If you have something to say, Ser Joffrey, speak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.98,0:51:51.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺爵士是我的心上人\N{\fs40}Ser Laenor is quite dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.15,0:51:55.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道公主对你来说也一样\N{\fs40}As I know the Princess is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.32,0:51:59.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该互相发誓保护他们\N{\fs40}We should swear to each other to guard them,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.87,0:52:03.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他们的秘密 如果他们安全……\N{\fs40}and their secrets, because if those are kept safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.08,0:52:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们也会平安无恙\N{\fs40}then so are we all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.60,0:52:29.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:33.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.36,0:52:37.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.59,0:52:53.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈尔温爵士 我可以借你的舞伴吗？\N{\fs40}May I, Ser Harwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.19,0:52:54.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然可以 王子\N{\fs40}Of course, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.39,0:53:04.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.86,0:53:59.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.08,0:54:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七层地狱啊 到底发生了什么？\N{\fs40}What in the Seven Hells is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.34,0:54:17.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺！\N{\fs40}Laenor!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.50,0:54:53.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,停下！\N{\fs40}Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.62,0:54:54.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉在哪里？\N{\fs40}Where's Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.73,0:55:16.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主？\N{\fs40}Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.32,0:55:28.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放我下来！\N{\fs40}Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.05,0:56:26.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七神之爱神圣永恒\N{\fs40}The love of the Seven is holy and eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.18,0:56:30.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,生命和爱的源泉\N{\fs40}The source of life and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.68,0:56:36.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今夜我们一同站在这里感恩赞美\N{\fs40}We stand here tonight in thanks and praise
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.14,0:56:39.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,两个灵魂合二为一\N{\fs40}to join two souls as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.82,0:56:46.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,天父……\N{\fs40}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.61,0:56:49.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,圣母……\N{\fs40}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.16,0:56:53.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,战士……\N{\fs40}Warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.79,0:56:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,铁匠……\N{\fs40}Smith...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.37,0:56:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,少女……\N{\fs40}Maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.54,0:57:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,老妪……\N{\fs40}Crone...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.71,0:57:03.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陌客\N{\fs40}Stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.30,0:57:07.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在请听他们的誓言\N{\fs40}Hear now their vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.63,0:57:12.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我属于你 你属于我\N{\fs40}I am yours and you are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.35,0:57:17.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论何至 此诺恒一\N{\fs40}Whatever may come.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.19,0:57:22.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我属于你 你属于我\N{\fs40}I am yours and you are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.57,0:57:24.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论何至 此诺恒一\N{\fs40}Whatever may come.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.78,0:57:30.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,于此 在诸神和世人见证下\N{\fs40}Here, in the presence of gods and men,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.24,0:57:31.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我宣布……\N{\fs40}I proclaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:35.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的兰尼诺\N{\fs40}Laenor of House Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.00,0:57:41.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和坦格利安家族的雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra of House Targaryen,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.54,0:57:43.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,结为夫妇\N{\fs40}to be man and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.09,0:57:49.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个躯体……\N{\fs40}One flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.97,0:57:51.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个心灵……\N{\fs40}one heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.55,0:57:54.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个魂魄……\N{\fs40}one soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.81,0:57:58.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,永恒不变\N{\fs40}now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.18,0:58:01.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Criston.
