Comment: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:39.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}布雷肯家族与布莱伍德家族自安达尔人入侵前便为世仇，\N布雷肯家族在安达尔人入侵后改信七神，而布莱伍德家族有着坚定的旧神信仰。
Comment: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.80,Note_rotation_Left_HOTD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(550,360)}穿上这个\N{\fs20}Kesommi aōle mīsās. \N\N{\fs30}推开挂毯后面的墙\N{\fs20}Rhakiāzmo inkot dōros indīs.\N\N{\fs30}沿着通道走\N{\fs20}Geltilio rȳ jās.\N\N{\fs30}我在外面等你\N{\fs20}Ninkiot avy rhaeninna.
Comment: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.07,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,只想独自生活\N{\fs40}Mērpāvose glaesilun.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.70,0:53:08.61,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.95,0:53:12.37,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你会在意我想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.45,0:53:14.62,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,这不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.70,0:53:18.21,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺是个好人 好骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.71,0:53:21.46,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,他会让你厌烦无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.63,0:53:25.92,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,婚姻只是一场政治安排 我听过这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.26,0:53:28.13,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,我的婚姻最近结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.76,0:53:30.09,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,那就带我走
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.51,0:53:32.14,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,这不是你一直以来的目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.43,0:53:36.64,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,我还没结婚 但时间正在飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.27,0:53:39.48,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,你肯定有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.23,0:53:44.07,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,从我父亲的御林铁卫中杀出一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.65,0:53:50.74,Subtitle_Valyrian_lower,,0,0,0,,带我去龙石岛让我成为你的妻子